---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Portfolio | MK Stock Lab" activePath="/portfolio">
  <header class="page-header">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Portfolio</p>
      <h1>Portfolio workspace shell</h1>
      <p class="lead">The portfolio rebuild will add multi-portfolio holdings, KRW/USD support, allocations, P/L, and rule-based risk notes.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="auth-required">
    <h2>Login-required area</h2>
    <p>Supabase Auth entry points are preserved in the header. Data schema and portfolio CRUD are intentionally deferred to later phases.</p>
    <ul class="status-list">
      <li><span>Base currency</span><strong>KRW</strong></li>
      <li><span>Supported currency</span><strong>USD</strong></li>
      <li><span>Portfolio AI Agent</span><strong class="neutral">Coming soon</strong></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Layout>
